        <h2>Game-Rules</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Everybody starts on the field in the top left corner</li>
            <li>The starting Player is decided at random</li>
            <li>If it's your turn you first roll your dice</li>
            <li>Red fields are easy questions</li>
            <li>Black fields are hard questions</li>
            <li>If you get the question correct you get points</li>
            <li>If you get the question wrong you get a penalty</li>
            <li>If you complete a round you get points</li>
            <li>The game ends if there are no more questions</li>
            <li>The game ends if one player has reached some amount of points</li>
